BarakattSpace Webstore – Software Requirements Specification (SRS)
1. Project Overview
BarakattSpace is a software development company providing software development services. The
BKWebstore is an online platform for selling products and building brand presence globally.
2. Functional Requirements
User registration/login, product browsing, cart, checkout, payment integration, order tracking, admin
panel.
3. Non-Functional Requirements
Fast performance, strong security, mobile responsiveness, scalability, multilingual support.
4. User Stories
Customers can browse, register, purchase, and track orders. Admin manages products and orders.

5. Entities
User, Product, ProductCategory, Order, Sale, Feedback
6. Constraints
Limited budget, 1-month timeline, regional payment 
